<plot>This film is about a song released by the New York City radio station, HOT 97. The song, entitled "The Tsunami Song", mocks Asian culture and makes fun of the victims of the devastating tsunami which destroyed many areas of Asia and killed thousands of people. The film examines the affects that the song had on Asian-American culture and why the release of the song never received mainstream media attention.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?620253</url></doc>
